My recommended 5B scope

Do exactly this and nothing more:

Use kickstart_template
Use kernel_args
Generate kickstarts only for implemented profiles
Add generated_kickstarts to status.json
Keep future profiles as safe placeholders

Then 5C can add richer template variables and more flexible kickstart rendering.